name: GO(working title) Beta
description:
How far will you GO?

GO(working title) is a minimalist, first-person,  five-lane endless style game that will test your reflexes and your patience.

GO is currently in Beta for testing and might have bugs. Feedback on the Beta would be appreciated!

At the moment there are only 7 areas and 2 practices areas. More will be added very soon.

Development Logs will be posted here when the game gets updated so be sure to check those out at the bottom of the page.

The final product will be available on Windows and Android on December 24th, 2019.

Thanks for testing!

-KoffeePunk
